I do believe that this is only the second time that US forces have killed or wounded the soldiers of an ally. The first time being in the Gulf War when an AH-64 Apache blew up a British Warrior IFV and killed 8 british soldiers while wounding 6 more.<br>
<br>
The US militray kills and wounds thier own soldiers all the time, not on purpose, training to fight a war is dangerous. There is a maximum emphesis on safety during exercises, but accidents happen. I spent 4 years in the Infantry, I know first hand how dangerous it can be.<br>
<br>
It is however something different when the Military forces of one nation accidently kill the military forces of another nation. There will be quite the flap over this.<br>
<br>
It is however a tragiady and my condolences go out to the families of thoes 4 dead and 8 wounded soldiers. As should yours. <p><center>LvL 60 Troll Oracle</center><center>SHOCK OF SWORDS</center><center>
